1982;;A Day in a Taxi (Une journée en taxi);;Canadian;;Robert Ménard;;Jean Yanne, Gilles Renaud, Monique Mercure;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A_Day_in_a_Taxi;;A man named Johnny (Renaud), who becomes the fall guy for a bank robbery, is released from prison on a 36-hour parole. He takes a taxi, driven by Michel (Yanne). During the road trip, Johnny has second thoughts and eventually Michel finds himself in the middle.